#

Apple Carrot Juice

5 min
$3.5
120 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-FreeLow-Calorie

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Drink

Tags:

JuiceHealthy DrinkRefreshing

Description

A refreshing and nutritious juice that combines sweet apples with vibrant carrots, perfect for a revitalizing drink!

Ingredients

  • apples: 2
  • carrots: 2
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
  • water: 1 cup
  • honey (optional): 1 tablespoon
